{"tid":1616693,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"原來幾年前咁多雙非嬰兒","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:19:30.000Z","uid":242674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bdba9e846bf00c5682309351facb40eac51fa1c2","tid":1616693,"uid":242674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYOx19w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYOx19w.gif&h=2f0bfde6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n03至13年多咗咁多嬰兒出世， 原來是因為雙非，即是 兩夫婦都係大陸人，來香港生仔。 怪不得現在通街都係細路。仲要啲細路啲行為好有中國大媽style （發音唔正、 成日旭身旭勢）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有冇人覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pj2VZZc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPj2VZZc.png&h=44b30eee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xa6PjZe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxa6PjZe.png&h=1868ad20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 2001年裁定中國公民在港所生嬰兒有居留權。 我想問：爲何這樣明顯的問題居然草議基本法時沒寫清楚？ 反而寫明每日有150個單程證？ 係咪特登唔寫明， 等終審法院審？  如果當年基本法禁雙非， 人口就唔會升得咁急， 我認為就唔洗起明日大嶼。 就沒大陸政府所謂&ldquo;深層次問題&rdquo;。 我覺得根本反送中係一個藉口畀政府來鬥地主， 其實目的是起多些樓，給新移民上公屋。"},{"pid":"c863e8f759a38d246bf717fb140d0a7fce8eebc9","tid":1616693,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:42:51.000Z","msg":"所以我好擔心之後幾年嘅後生全部俾人洗腦 真正香港人生嘅細路又唔夠多"},{"pid":"d52d879b268418b63cfeac5a9cbd79ac1c436a21","tid":1616693,"uid":242674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9cW0rP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9cW0rP6.png&h=3d5f0714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u05TMP7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu05TMP7.png&h=9365f471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1utmVJt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1utmVJt.gif&h=c6cede8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsources:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/statistics/data/10/27/112.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fstatistics%2Fdata%2F10%2F27%2F112.html&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=e7c18786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/statistics/data/10/27/112.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/fd.jsp?file=B71812FA2018XXXXB0100.pdf&amp;product_id=FA100090&amp;lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Ffd.jsp%3Ffile%3DB71812FA2018XXXXB0100.pdf%26product_id%3DFA100090%26lang%3D2&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=d6799d4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/fd.jsp?file=B71812FA2018XXXXB0100.pdf&amp;product_id=FA100090&amp;lang=2</a>"},{"pid":"f7609a354f6933ab396196b7cfdfb09e3c79cb94","tid":1616693,"uid":242674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:29:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1625899e8992a134e7bb1274b1dbc6eaa2e89018","tid":1616693,"uid":242674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"push"}]}